    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been absolutely wonderful to own. It's in great shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. I've taken really good care of it, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner today. If you're looking for a smooth, dependable car that still looks sharp, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
