      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been maintained to a high standard of mechanical and aesthetic integrity. It offers a refined driving experience, characterized by consistent performance and a well-preserved interior. Thoroughly vetted by our technicians, this offering represents a superior value proposition for the discerning driver who prioritizes reliability and professional upkeep.",
      "price": 36800.0,
