      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really solid shape! It runs beautifully and has been well-maintained over the years. It's perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle that's ready for many more road trips. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
