    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2008 Porsche Cayman S, powered by the mid-mounted 3.4L M97 flat-six paired with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. This example features a factory-spec limited-slip differential and has been maintained with a focus on lateral dynamics; the suspension utilizes refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers for optimal damping curves. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul with a low-temperature thermostat to manage thermal loads during spirited driving. The drivetrain remains dry, and the shift linkage is exceptionally tight, offering the tactile feedback synonymous with the 987 chassis. While the exterior shows minor stone peppering consistent with its mileage, the structural integrity and high-revving performance of the naturally aspirated boxer engine are superlative.",
